cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper deals with MIMO cognitive radio systems, which involve wireless communication and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves learning algorithms and convergence analysis, which are common topics in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with interference management, which is a common topic in cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Finally, the paper involves some numerical simulations, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
